metadata.name: Meta Verse
metadata.description:
ART WORK BY @AMORSCASH

METAVERSE CITY, IN THE ALLEY WAYS SMOKIN' CORPORATION COMIN UP, WE ALL LOSIN FOCUS MANEUVER THROUGH THE CITY I BEEN LITTY, I JUST DOVE IN THE PROPS THEY AIN'T GIVE ME I'M INSULTED BEFORE I RAPPED, I WOULD WRAP GAS UP IN A BAG AIN'T NO CAP, THATS A FACT WE KNEW HOW TO ADAPT I BEEN DIFFERENT, AS FAR AS WHAT I THINK ABOUT THEM I'M INDIFFERENT I'M DEAD SET ON GETTING THE PEN LIFTED DIRTY DOZEN AT THE TOP AIN'T SUPPLYIN US AND THE COPS GOT THE DROPS AND THEY EYE ON US JUST SURVIVING THE TIMES, I'M FEELING FINE, WHEN I'M HIGH AND I'M FLYING, I THINK I'M OUTTA MY MIND YO POPULATION ZERO, TECHNOLOGY ALIGNED WITH THE HUMAN KIND FOR THAT MONEY, GREEN, DINERO ITS ALL THE KILLERS THAT DELIVER THE PEACE, THEY LEAVE THE BODIES AS THEY LITTER THE STREETS QUESTION IS, WHO BE SINNING THE LEAST?

WILL THEY KNOW (ANOTHER DAY, ANOTHER WAY) KNOW MY NAME .../ (AND EVERYTHING I GOTTA SAY) I DON'T KNOW ... (BEFORE I GO, I WANNA LIVE) JUST PLAY THE GAME.../ (AND NOT REGRET WHAT I DID) SAVE MY SOUL ... (IN THE CITY WHERE THERE'S MANY OF US) SHOW MY PAIN.../ (WHERE THEY AIN'T NEVER WANTED ANY OF US) WHEN I GO... (WILL YOU FEEL IT WHEN I'M GONE?) I'LL MAKE A CHANGE.../ (AND I'LL PUT THAT IN A SONG...)
